<c.white><c.mono_sans>almost to a fault,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

622
00:24:34.083 --> 00:24:37.333  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and they have great pride</c.mono_sans></c.white>

623
00:24:34.083 --> 00:24:37.333  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>in their ways.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

624
00:24:39.333 --> 00:24:40.667  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You're the Captain?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

625
00:24:40.667 --> 00:24:42.166  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:32.86%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We're ready.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

626
00:24:42.166 --> 00:24:43.542  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>This way, please.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

627
00:24:58.625 --> 00:25:02.000  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:67.14%  line:73.96% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Welcome to our world, Captain.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

628
00:24:58.625 --> 00:25:02.000  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Thank you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

629
00:25:02.000 --> 00:25:05.125  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:63.33%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We regret that our system of</c.mono_sans></c.white>

630
00:25:02.000 --> 00:25:05.125  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>justice is troubling you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

631
00:25:05.125 --> 00:25:07.917  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>The boy, Wesley Crusher,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

632
00:25:05.125 --> 00:25:07.917  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>where is he, please?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

633
00:25:07.917 --> 00:25:09.875  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:27.14%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>In accord</c.mono_sans></c.white>

634
00:25:07.917 --> 00:25:09.875  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>with the Prime Directive,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

635
00:25:09.875 --> 00:25:12.750  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I've allowed them to hold him</c.mono_sans></c.white>

636
00:25:09.875 --> 00:25:12.750  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:63.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>pending the outcome of this.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

637
00:25:12.750 --> 00:25:15.291  position:50.00%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>He is safe</c.mono_sans></c.white>

638
00:25:12.750 --> 00:25:15.291  position:50.00%,start  align:start size:34.76%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and unharmed.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

639
00:25:15.291 --> 00:25:16.875  position:50.00%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We promise that.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

640
00:25:16.875 --> 00:25:20.375  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Captain Picard, I do not</c.mono_sans></c.white>

641
00:25:16.875 --> 00:25:20.375  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>know how you Earth people</c.mono_sans></c.white>

642
00:25:20.375 --> 00:25:22.083  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>conduct law and justice--</c.mono_sans></c.white>

643
00:25:22.083 --> 00:25:24.500  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>even if you respect</c.mono_sans></c.white>

644
00:25:22.083 --> 00:25:24.500  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:32.86%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>such things.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

645
00:25:24.500 --> 00:25:26.125  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:21.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We do.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

646
00:25:26.125 --> 00:25:28.458  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Good. So do we.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

647
00:25:28.458 --> 00:25:32.500  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Our precepts have been</c.mono_sans></c.white>

648
00:25:28.458 --> 00:25:32.500  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:59.52%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>handed down from long ago.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

649
00:25:32.500 --> 00:25:35.834  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:59.52%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>The tranquility you see in</c.mono_sans></c.white>

650
00:25:32.500 --> 00:25:35.834  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:70.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>our lives has been made possible</c.mono_sans></c.white>

651
00:25:35.834 --> 00:25:37.166  position:57.62%,start  align:start size:32.86%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>by our laws.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

652
00:25:37.166 --> 00:25:38.917  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:21.43%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>RIVAN:</c.mono_sans></c.white>

653
00:25:37.166 --> 00:25:38.917  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We are a people of law.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

654
00:25:38.917 --> 00:25:41.208  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>They do sometimes</c.mono_sans></c.white>

655
00:25:38.917 --> 00:25:41.208  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>bring us sadness,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

656
00:25:41.208 --> 00:25:44.041  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but we have learned</c.mono_sans></c.white>

657
00:25:41.208 --> 00:25:44.041  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to adjust to that.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

658
00:25:44.041 --> 00:25:46.250  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Perhaps your laws</c.mono_sans></c.white>

659
00:25:44.041 --> 00:25:46.250  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:34.76%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>work as well?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

660
00:25:46.250 --> 00:25:49.542  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>They haven't always,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

661
00:25:46.250 --> 00:25:49.542  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but now they do.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

662
00:25:49.542 --> 00:25:51.834  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Do you execute criminals?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

663
00:25:51.834 --> 00:25:54.125  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No, not any longer.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

664
00:25:54.125 --> 00:25:55.500  position:48.10%,start  align:start size:21.43%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>RIVAN:</c.mono_sans></c.white>

665
00:25:54.125 --> 00:25:55.500  position:48.10%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But you did once?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

666
00:25:55.500 --> 00:25:58.375  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Unfortunately, yes.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

667
00:25:55.500 --> 00:25:58.375  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But since then...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

668
00:25:58.375 --> 00:26:01.250  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And when you did, was it</c.mono_sans></c.white>

669
00:25:58.375 --> 00:26:01.250  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:63.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>believed necessary to do so?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

670
00:26:02.792 --> 00:26:05.333  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Some people felt</c.mono_sans></c.white>

671
00:26:02.792 --> 00:26:05.333  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>that it was necessary,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

672
00:26:05.333 --> 00:26:08.709  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but we have learned to detect</c.mono_sans></c.white>

673
00:26:05.333 --> 00:26:08.709  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:69.05%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>the seeds of criminal behavior.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

674
00:26:08.709 --> 00:26:11.375  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Capital punishment,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

675
00:26:08.709 --> 00:26:11.375  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:34.76%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>in our world,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

676
00:26:11.375 --> 00:26:14.333  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>is no longer considered</c.mono_sans></c.white>

677
00:26:11.375 --> 00:26:14.333  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>a justifiable deterrent.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

678
00:26:14.333 --> 00:26:16.792  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:19.52%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>So...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

679
00:26:16.792 --> 00:26:19.875  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>we are not yet</c.mono_sans></c.white>

680
00:26:16.792 --> 00:26:19.875  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>as advanced as they are.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

681
00:26:21.709 --> 00:26:24.458  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:59.52%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And since you are advanced</c.mono_sans></c.white>

682
00:26:21.709 --> 00:26:24.458  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>in other ways, too,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

683
00:26:24.458 --> 00:26:28.333  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:69.05%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I suggest you use your superior</c.mono_sans></c.white>

684
00:26:24.458 --> 00:26:28.333  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:70.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>powers to rescue the Wesley boy.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

685
00:26:28.333 --> 00:26:31.166  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We will record him</c.mono_sans></c.white>

686
00:26:28.333 --> 00:26:31.166  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:84.62% 
