687
00:26:31.166 --> 00:26:32.834  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>out of our reach--</c.mono_sans></c.white>

688
00:26:32.834 --> 00:26:36.458  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:67.14%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>an advanced person who luckily</c.mono_sans></c.white>

689
00:26:32.834 --> 00:26:36.458  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>escaped the barbarism</c.mono_sans></c.white>

690
00:26:36.458 --> 00:26:38.709  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:67.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>of this backward little world.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

691
00:26:38.709 --> 00:26:43.041  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:63.33%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Unfortunately, we have a law</c.mono_sans></c.white>

692
00:26:38.709 --> 00:26:43.041  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>known as the Prime Directive.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

693
00:26:43.041 --> 00:26:45.583  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Riker has explained it to us.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

694
00:26:46.959 --> 00:26:50.875  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Is the boy in any danger</c.mono_sans></c.white>

695
00:26:46.959 --> 00:26:50.875  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>from you at this moment?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

696
00:26:52.959 --> 00:26:55.166  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Until sundown?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

697
00:26:57.208 --> 00:26:59.709  position:53.81%,start  align:start size:30.95%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Because you</c.mono_sans></c.white>

698
00:26:57.208 --> 00:26:59.709  position:53.81%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>are strangers,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

699
00:26:59.709 --> 00:27:01.917  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>we are delaying</c.mono_sans></c.white>

700
00:26:59.709 --> 00:27:01.917  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>enforcement of the law,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

701
00:27:01.917 --> 00:27:04.709  position:50.00%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but we must act</c.mono_sans></c.white>

702
00:27:01.917 --> 00:27:04.709  position:50.00%,start  align:start size:30.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>by sundown.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

703
00:27:04.709 --> 00:27:06.917  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Then I have another question.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

704
00:27:06.917 --> 00:27:10.709  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:69.05%  line:79.29% 
