706
00:27:10.709 --> 00:27:14.542  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>as we do, we have</c.mono_sans></c.white>

707
00:27:10.709 --> 00:27:14.542  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>encountered a strange object.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

708
00:27:14.542 --> 00:27:17.875  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>A vessel, perhaps.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

709
