00:27:20.333 --> 00:27:22.875  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>It's not entirely real.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

711
00:27:22.875 --> 00:27:26.834  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>At least it's not</c.mono_sans></c.white>

712
00:27:22.875 --> 00:27:26.834  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>completely solid.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

