00:27:29.834 --> 00:27:32.250  position:50.00%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Do you mean God?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

714
00:27:32.250 --> 00:27:34.333  position:46.19%,start  align:start size:17.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>God?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

715
00:27:34.333 --> 00:27:37.375  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>God is said to be</c.mono_sans></c.white>

716
00:27:34.333 --> 00:27:37.375  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>somewhere up there</c.mono_sans></c.white>

717
00:27:37.375 --> 00:27:39.083  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>protecting us.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

718
00:27:39.083 --> 00:27:41.083  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Exactly...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

719
00:27:41.083 --> 00:27:43.417  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>exactly how would you</c.mono_sans></c.white>

720
00:27:41.083 --> 00:27:43.417  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:34.76%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>describe God?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

721
00:27:43.417 --> 00:27:44.959  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>As you just did.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

722
00:27:44.959 --> 00:27:48.417  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>As existing both here</c.mono_sans></c.white>

723
00:27:44.959 --> 00:27:48.417  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and in another place, also.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

724
00:27:48.417 --> 00:27:52.500  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But when God wants to</c.mono_sans></c.white>

